short_description: DescriptionIsn’t it amazing how even a small object can get up in the air and stay there! Follow in the footsteps of great inventors and make these eight fun models. All you need are easily availa...
description: Description Isn’t it amazing how even a small object can get up in the air and stay there! Follow in the footsteps of great inventors and make these eight fun models. All you need are easily available bits and pieces, plus things you usually recycle. Simple step-by-step instructions and clear photographs show you how to make a glider that can cruise along for 30 metres, an airship from a helium balloon and a propeller, a high-flying box kite, an ornithopter with bird-like wings, and more. Key points • Incredible facts explaining how the these vehicles are built and work. • Easy-to-follow guides to make a whole range of working models. • Great resource for school projects using simple household items. description: First 100 Trucks Your little one will love to discover the incredible trucks and things that go inside this bright board book. There are 100 different truck photographs to look at and talk about, and 100 truck names to read and learn, too. The pages are made from tough board for hours of fun reading, and the cover is softly padded for little hands to hold. Giá sản phẩm trên Tiki đã bao gồm thuế theo luật hiện hành. Bên cạnh đó, tuỳ vào loại sản phẩm, hình thức và địa chỉ giao hàng mà có thể phát sinh thêm chi phí khác như phí vận chuyển, phụ phí hàng cồng kềnh, thuế nhập khẩu (đối với đơn hàng giao từ nước ngoài có giá trị trên 1 triệu đồng).....
